A production-grade DevOps project implementing a complete microservices architecture using **Python, Docker, Docker Compose .
This project demonstrates how to design, build, test, containerize, orchestrate, and monitor a modern cloud-native application.

---

## ğŸš€ Project Overview

Cloud-Ninjas is a full-stack microservices platform consisting of:

| Service          | Technology                                        |
| ---------------- | ------------------------------------------------- |
| Frontend         | Python (Streamlit)                                |
| Backend          | Python (FastAPI)                                  |
| Database Service | Python (FastAPI + SQLAlchemy)                     |
| Database         | MySQL 8                                           |
| Cache            | Redis                                             |

